{"tid":1053927,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"過去一年磨過 2xx 把刀 你問我答 (2)","createTime":"2019-03-09T12:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:36:46.000Z","uid":101575,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d258f0422cfaba8c6aae2e72939166d717e3186a","tid":1053927,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"由於上一個post出現左D誤會同埋沉底<br />\n我就係到整理一下之前打既文章<br />\n上一個post 既 link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1048029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1048029/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澄清翻:我唔係Alan 我唔係KTH Kitchen<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n是咁的，喺廚藝學院讀緊嘅時候，學校啲刀 9 成都係鈍到阿媽都唔認得, 每日都要拎住把間尺同啲食材搏命，久而久之終於頂唔順，萌生要磨刀嘅諗法。<br />\n<br />\n但問題係，我唔識。<br />\n<br />\n我開始會問下阿 sir 點磨，不過用完阿 sir 教既方法都無咩用。所以我就開始上網搵資料、睇片、爬文，再不停用學校屋企嘅刀實習。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我得到磨刀技能一個。自此我就開始每日幫屋企人、朋友、親戚、街坊磨刀&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAny肥，我喺幫人磨刀嘅過程發現, 普遍香港人對於「刀」嘅知識係接近零。<br />\n<br />\n例如真係有好多人唔知刀係有得磨，覺得係消耗品, 用鈍咗就會買把新。<br />\n有啲就用咗幾十年都無磨過把刀，日日都係會用把鐵尺壓開啲食物。<br />\n多數家庭主婦或者 home cook 認識刀具嘅牌子, 都停留喺係孖X牌同陳X記。<br />\n<br />\n所以我就想喺到, 拋磚引玉, 講下一 D 刀嘅知識, 等連登仔唔使再俾人搵笨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e3b69cd80cdaa0b355fc5c33480386f727638e","tid":1053927,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"咁我就講下D簡單野先<br />\n<br />\n世上咁多唔同刀型<br />\n中式有「片刀」、「文武刀」...<br />\n西式有「主廚刀 (Chef&rsquo;s knife)」、「牛刀」...<br />\n日式有「出刃」、「柳刃」...<br />\n仲有好多好多...<br />\n<br />\n到底我要需要咩刀呢?<br />\n<br />\n其實一般屋企用嘅話, 我會推薦用<br />\n「三德刀」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dahg89d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDahg89d.jpg&h=24684ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「主廚刀」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiDwdAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiDwdAX.jpg&h=25a056dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「文武刀」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7mmAPk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7mmAPk.jpg&h=fe4291b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為屋企處理食材相對簡單, 唔需要針對特別嘅食材, 要用特別嘅刀<br />\n所以家用刀會以萬用 or 多用途做首要條件<br />\n依三種刀功能上都差唔多, 切片、條、絲、丁、粒都無問題<br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅分別在於唔同既切野手法<br />\n「文武刀」同「三德刀」傾向平推嘅切法<br />\n而主廚刀就傾向Rock Chop (Gordon Ramsay 嗰種切法)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5z_d0soK1cI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5z_d0soK1cI&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=96a08a3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5z_d0soK1cI</a> (12分鐘個到)<br />\n<br />\n所以只係睇你慣用咩手勢切野, 無話邊種好D<br />\n而家搵一種適合你, 或者你鍾意嘅手勢"},{"pid":"1df95f557a5ed4527f073cde25bb6706b541a1d8","tid":1053927,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"上面講左刀型既分別，咁下面講深入少少<br />\n<br />\n我地成日聽「不鏽鋼」乜「不鏽鋼」乜<br />\n其實不鏽鋼只係一個鋼材種類，不鏽鋼入面有多唔同既鋼<br />\n例如 VG10 AUS8 1.14116....... N百種<br />\n但簡單D講白D，其實係硬度既分別。<br />\n<br />\n硬度單位係HRC (Rockwell hardness)<br />\n數字愈大愈硬，反之亦然。<br />\n同常用係廚刀上既硬度介乎53-67 左右<br />\n愈硬就鋒利度保持得愈耐，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係愈硬愈好，因為愈硬=愈脆<br />\n所以愈硬既刀泛用性愈低<br />\n軟身鋼就易鈍D，不過佢唔易崩，斬骨無問題<br />\n<br />\n所以講到尾都係睇自己需要，無絕對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6306d1128088261af9c2e1e5c515e5fc1e20c9db","tid":1053927,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"好多人問xxx牌子點睇，xxxbudget有咩選擇<br />\n其實好難一刀切答到你yes or no <br />\n<br />\n所以我係到講一講點樣選擇岩自己既刀<br />\n<br />\n首先我會分開4樣野<br />\n鋼材、刀型、外觀、單刃/雙刃<br />\n<br />\n單刃刀只會係日本既刀上出現<br />\n例如柳刃、出刃、菜切<br />\n<br />\n而雙刃就係一般西式刀，中菜刀<br />\n例如主廚刀、三德刀、片刀<br />\n<br />\n不過有d刀形係單鋒同雙鋒都有<br />\n牛刀、菜刀、出刃等等<br />\n<br />\n兩者有幾個切野上既分別<br />\n<br />\n由於係單刃既原因，單鋒刀切野時會把刀會傾向食材個面，所以一開始唔慣既話，會切唔到直線。<br />\n相反雙刃就易好多操作<br />\n<br />\n而且單刃一般都會用高炭鋼打造(即係好易生鏽)<br />\n<br />\n仲有係磨刀上，單刃同雙刃磨既方法唔同<br />\n<br />\n不過單刃最大既好處就係佢設計上，背面有一個坑，令到切野食時唔會黏刀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVgYC5M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVgYC5M.png&h=c4bd6009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一般家用其實會單刃門檻比較高(切野唔慣or因為用高炭鋼打造好易生鏽)所以我都會建議買雙刃刀。"},{"pid":"72f7af9f1cedebbef57e2a706e9834309e497534","tid":1053927,"uid":101575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"相信好多人都睇過個日本人用好多奇怪野整刀<br />\n（啫喱、朱古力、麵包.......）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg3qsVzHeUt5_cPpcRtoaJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCg3qsVzHeUt5_cPpcRtoaJQ&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=f7ca6ca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg3qsVzHeUt5_cPpcRtoaJQ</a><br />\n<br />\n但一般我地緊係唔會用個d野造刀<br />\n<br />\n市面上買到既廚刀主要係用以下三種材料造<br />\n<br />\n「不鏽鋼」<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcjO0jZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcjO0jZ.jpg&h=7015c99b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「高炭鋼」<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8SpyFn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8SpyFn.jpg&h=e26ee4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「陶瓷」<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVrxHyV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVrxHyV.jpg&h=5fd673b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先講「不鏽鋼」<br />\n<br />\n「不鏽鋼」係最普及造刀既材料<br />\n主要原因係易於打理，好難生鏽。<br />\n但都係有機會生鏽，如果成日濕住把刀又唔抹乾<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係同樣條「不鏽鋼」，級數可以差好遠<br />\n所以有大量既刀都係用平價「不鏽鋼」造，咁成本就平好多。<br />\n<br />\n常見既「不鏽鋼」由軟至硬分別有<br />\n<br />\n「304 鋼」 &lt; <br />\n<br />\n「1.4116鋼 ，例子：孖人牌」&lt;<br />\n<br />\n「九鉻鋼/9cr15 mov」 &lt; <br />\n<br />\n「vg10 鋼， 例子： 藤次郎 dp系列 」 &lt;<br />\n<br />\n「SG2鋼，例子：高村作」&lt;<br />\n<br />\n「zdp189鋼，例子：佑成」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價錢由幾十去到幾千都有<br />\n<br />\n通常硬度同價錢係成正比<br />\n<br />\n因為愈硬就保持鋒利度愈耐，同埋可以磨得更薄（即係更利），所以最硬個d都係土豪玩物。<br />\n<br />\n講住依到先，一陣再打"},{"pid":"c077b7e5a8b97555a332f32816cabfe5dbb95594","tid":1053927,"uid":101575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"我發現好多人問一樣野<br />\nxxx號磨刀石加xxx號磨刀石得唔得<br />\n我skip左幾多號又得唔得<br />\n<br />\n首先大家要明白一樣野 （個人見解，不喜可插）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">世界上對於鋒利度係無標準<br />\n<br />\n世上係無1，2，3，4，5，6，7，8，9鋒利度</span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家問xxx號得唔得，其實自己諗下「得唔得係指咩得唔得？」<br />\n<br />\n切肉片得唔得？<br />\n切蕃茄片得唔得？<br />\n切a4紙得唔得？<br />\n切報紙得唔得?<br />\n斷髮得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n大家自己想追求咩地步只有自己先知<br />\n<br />\n再講深一層<br />\n比如我話1000/3000，得！<br />\n就會有人話，唔得！都斷唔到髮<br />\n<br />\n假如我再講1000/5000/8000/12000，得！<br />\n又會有人話，無意義，上到12000俾你切幾分鐘咪又係無左個鋒利度<br />\n<br />\n所以當大家背後係唔唔同目的，但個問題都係「得唔得」，我就答你唔到架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4aa0f61b3ce59f7d16a7ebac999f2a08b5abcc","tid":1053927,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:58:33.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"7eceeb304a8efa9cbc9d2019c03b293be495337c","tid":1053927,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:05:23.000Z","msg":"正呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317de7b4d80e861981ebe0eacc40e26ffe786547","tid":1053927,"uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:12:08.000Z","msg":"Wa ! Lm"},{"pid":"32f3edd439f0878b8f3fd4e0660ba5679761d5c9","tid":1053927,"uid":22692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"點解要扮KTH"},{"pid":"85b92495305beb65713bc48b29c257213743c04e","tid":1053927,"uid":101575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32f3edd439f0878b8f3fd4e0660ba5679761d5c9","tid":1053927,"uid":22692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"點解要扮KTH"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201